data.title: Not a very good lunch
data.text: It had been many years since my last visit, and I know why now.   Wow, that was not good.  Food quality was poor to say the least.  The meat was burnt and dry.  The bread was hard.  The sauces are poorly constructed.  I would not go back.  And the prices are not cheap.

data.title: Lunch.
data.text:
It's called Fiesta burrito,
Steak is not good. Reminds me of dog food. Seemed cold and old. 
Guacamole over priced, too much tomatoes, onion and cilantro. 
Place is clean and decorated nicely. 
Huge menu. Might try again, but I would not order the steak again.
